{"tid":1876711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《Let It Be》贈港人　湯家驊：香港太多負能量　從今起每天送大家一首歌","createTime":"2020-02-12T14:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T22:21:43.000Z","uid":97944,"like":4,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"178f7c3d3e95fa8309245fdb7f0bbd8931af31e4","tid":1876711,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200212-19_KgldJ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200212-19_KgldJ_1200x0.png&h=5d097940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在香港陷入一片口罩荒之際，行會成員、資深大律師湯家驊為港人帶來了一線曙光。他今日在 FB 表示香港「實在太多負能量」，從今日開始他會每天送一首歌予香港，希望大家能走出陰霾。他為香港人帶來的第一首歌，是披頭四的《Let It Be》。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊近日多次開腔評論應付疫情的對策。對於醫護罷工事件，他曾形容是「有人把政治立場放高於專業職守，有人為了救人自願冒險服務社㑹」，認為大家應尊重及珍惜這自我選擇的權利。至於有輿論要求管制口罩價格，湯家驊近日接受傳媒訪問時，就質疑這樣反而會減低供應商供貨誘因，有違自由市場原則。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/let-it-be-%E8%B4%88%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E8%B2%A0%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F-%E5%BE%9E%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E9%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96%E6%AD%8C/?fbclid=IwAR2Miztev-YI9JjcbAGIZxbjGX97Cy2IYmJBupgTovkcI7YAMxJ9u67HyNo#.XkQMu4VqYhw.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Flet-it-be-%25E8%25B4%2588%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2587%258F-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AD%258C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2Miztev-YI9JjcbAGIZxbjGX97Cy2IYmJBupgTovkcI7YAMxJ9u67HyNo%23.XkQMu4VqYhw.facebook&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=31660033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=h